OL,3,CStormont leaders call for answers over
OL,4,Cvetting of former police ombudsman
OL,6,FStormont's leaders have called for
OL,7,Furgent answers around the security
OL,8,Fvetting process involved in the
OL,9,Fappointment of a former police
OL,10,Fombudsman in Northern Ireland.
OL,12,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill and
OL,13,Fdeputy First Minister Emma Little
OL,14,FPengelly urged the Government to
OL,15,Fprovide clarity after DUP leader Gavin
OL,16,FRobinson claimed Marie Anderson had
OL,17,Fbeen appointed to the role in 2019
OL,18,F"despite security concerns".
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
