CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776870667
OL,3,CStormont leaders call for answers over
OL,4,Cvetting of former police ombudsman
OL,6,FMs Anderson, who was responsible for
OL,7,Finvestigating complaints against
OL,8,Fpolice officers, retired from the role
OL,9,Fat the end of 2025.
OL,11,FMr Robinson raised concerns in the
OL,12,FHouse of Commons on Monday as Prime
OL,13,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer answered
OL,14,Fquestions from MPs about the security
OL,15,Fvetting around Lord Peter Mandelson's
OL,16,Fappointment as US ambassador.
OL,18,FLord Mandelson was sacked in September
OL,19,Flast year after revelations about the
OL,20,Fextent of his relationship with
OL,21,Fdisgraced financier Jeffrey Epstein.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776870667
OL,3,CStormont leaders call for answers over
OL,4,Cvetting of former police ombudsman
OL,6,FMr Robinson said it was "incredible to
OL,7,Flearn that in Northern Ireland a
OL,8,Fpolitical appointment was made
OL,9,Ffollowing the refusal to clear an
OL,10,Findividual for security access".
OL,12,FThe DUP leader said Ms Anderson had
OL,13,Fengaged in legacy issues in the region
OL,14,F"despite Security Service concerns".
OL,16,FHe called for the former ombudsman's
OL,17,Fappointment to be examined as part of
OL,18,Fthe broader review into security
OL,19,Fvetting instigated by the Prime
OL,20,FMinister.
OL,26,@nD@YOUrD@_O]vD@AOUvD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776870667
OL,3,CStormont leaders call for answers over
OL,4,Cvetting of former police ombudsman
OL,6,FThe First Minister and deputy First
OL,7,FMinister were asked about the issue as
OL,8,Fthey spoke to reporters in Belfast on
OL,9,FTuesday.
OL,11,FSinn Fein vice president Ms O'Neill
OL,12,Fhighlighted that Ms Anderson's
OL,13,Fappointment was made directly by the
OL,14,FUK Government as it happened at a time
OL,15,Fwhen the Stormont Executive was in a
OL,16,Fperiod of collapse.
OL,18,F"So it's for them to provide clarity
OL,19,Fin terms of the process that they
OL,20,Ffollowed, including the safeguarding
OL,21,Felements to all of that," she said.
OL,26,@zD@AOU}D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776870667
OL,3,CStormont leaders call for answers over
OL,4,Cvetting of former police ombudsman
OL,6,F"So I think the clarity that's
OL,7,Frequired needs to come. Because
OL,8,Fthere's been a lot of speculation. And
OL,9,FI don't think that's helpful for
OL,10,Feither the individual involved or for
OL,11,Fanybody involved in the process.
OL,13,F"So I think the sooner there's
OL,14,Fclarity, I think that will be a better
OL,15,Fplace for us to reach, as opposed to
OL,16,Ffeeding speculation whenever people
OL,17,Fperhaps have half of the truth or
OL,18,Fperhaps not all of the information."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776870667
OL,3,CStormont leaders call for answers over
OL,4,Cvetting of former police ombudsman
OL,6,FShe added: "So I think we need to be
OL,7,Fcrystal clear, and I think the public
OL,8,Fdeserve to have the answers that have
OL,9,Fnow been speculated about because of
OL,10,Fsome public commentary. So I think
OL,11,Fit's for the Secretary of State
OL,12,F(Hilary Benn) to actually provide that
OL,13,Fclarity, to give people the assurances
OL,14,Fthat they're looking for."
OL,16,FDUP Assembly member Ms Little-Pengelly
OL,17,Fsaid her party leader had raised
OL,18,F"really serious and important issues".
OL,26,@nD@LOUvD@ZO]zD@AOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776870667
OL,3,CStormont leaders call for answers over
OL,4,Cvetting of former police ombudsman
OL,6,F"We've seen this issue rolled out over
OL,7,Fthe last number of days over in
OL,8,FWestminster in relation to Peter
OL,9,FMandelson," she said.
OL,11,F"I think when a whistleblower comes
OL,12,Fforward with information that this has
OL,13,Fpotentially happened here in relation
OL,14,Fto a very high-profile and sensitive
OL,15,Fpost ` a post where that person will
OL,16,Fhave access to a significant amount of
OL,17,Fvery high-level and secure data `
OL,18,Fthen, of course, that needs to be
OL,19,Fcalled out ` that has been done by my
OL,20,Fparty leader, Gavin Robinson.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@KO]sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776870667
OL,3,CStormont leaders call for answers over
OL,4,Cvetting of former police ombudsman
OL,6,F"And we need to get to the truth of
OL,7,Fthis. If there is truth in this
OL,8,Fallegation, then that then needs to
OL,9,Fcome forward. We need to investigate
OL,10,Fand it needs to be investigated fully.
OL,12,F"I think my party leader was asking
OL,13,Ffor this issue to be included in terms
OL,14,Fof this review about how this security
OL,15,Fvetting works.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776870667
OL,3,CStormont leaders call for answers over
OL,4,Cvetting of former police ombudsman
OL,6,F"I have to say, I think it would be
OL,7,Fabsolutely preposterous to suggest
OL,8,Fthat we shouldn't have that kind of
OL,9,Fhigh-level vetting for these secure
OL,10,Fposts in Northern Ireland because of
OL,11,Fsome kind of political or other
OL,12,Fagenda. Of course we need that.
OL,14,F"That vetting is there to ensure that
OL,15,Fthose people with access to very high-
OL,16,Flevel and secure information have the
OL,17,Fappropriate clearances, that they are
OL,18,Fappropriate people with integrity in
OL,19,Forder to access that.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776870667
OL,3,CStormont leaders call for answers over
OL,4,Cvetting of former police ombudsman
OL,6,F"So yes, we do need to get answers. We
OL,7,Fneed to get those urgently. Of course,
OL,8,Fthis was a direct rule appointment at
OL,9,Fthe time that none of us were involved
OL,10,Fin that. But we do need those answers,
OL,11,Fand we need them urgently."
OL,13,FResponding to Mr Robinson's call on
OL,14,FMonday, Sir Keir said: "I will ensure
OL,15,Fthe review covers all the relevant
OL,16,Fissues and material and I will take
OL,17,Finto account what he has just said."
OL,19,FA Northern Ireland Office spokesperson
OL,20,Fsaid: "Marie Anderson was appointed in
OL,21,F2019 by the then secretary of state.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@[O]vD@XOUyD@dO]|D@GOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
