OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776870667
OL,3,CStormont leaders call for answers over
OL,4,Cvetting of former police ombudsman
OL,6,F"We are looking into our records and
OL,7,Fwill respond as soon as possible.
OL,9,F"The Prime Minister has also confirmed
OL,10,Fthis matter will be included as part
OL,11,Fof the Fulford review."
OL,13,FThe office of the Police Ombudsman has
OL,14,Fbeen approached for comment.
